### Get All Reviews
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Reviews with Filters (e.g., source=hostaway, rating=5)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews?source=hostaway&rating=5
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Reviews with Search (e.g., for "great")
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews?search=great
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Reviews with Tags (e.g., "featured")
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews?tags=featured
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Reviews with Pagination (e.g., page 1, limit 2)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews?page=1&limit=2
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Trends Data (e.g., for 180 days)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/trends?range=180d
Content-Type: application/json

### Get All Tags
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/tags
Content-Type: application/json

### Create a New Custom Tag
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "NewCustomTag"
}

### Delete a Custom Tag (replace with actual tag ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/tags/custom-tag-id-123
Content-Type: application/json

### Get a Single Review (e.g., Hostaway review with ID 1)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/hostaway/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Update a Review (Approve)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/hostaway/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approved": true
}

### Update a Review (Show on Web)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/hostaway/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "selectedForWeb": true
}

### Add a Tag to a Review (e.g., "featured")
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/hostaway/1/tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tag": "featured"
}

### Remove a Tag from a Review (e.g., "featured")
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/hostaway/1/tags/featured
Content-Type: application/json

### Bulk Approve Reviews
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/bulk-approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reviewIds": [
    {"source": "hostaway", "id": "1"},
    {"source": "google", "id": "g1"}
  ]
}

### Bulk Show on Web Reviews
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/bulk-show
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reviewIds": [
    {"source": "hostaway", "id": "1"},
    {"source": "google", "id": "g1"}
  ]
}

### Get Approved Reviews (for property page)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/approved
Content-Type: application/json
